description:
What could be more fun than good old classic shooting? Now you don't have to go to the range to shoot!

Realistic interiors will immerse you in the atmosphere of a shooting range, and you will feel the excitement of owning weapons. A variety of tasks will not let you get bored and will be a real test of your accuracy.

A beginner will quickly master the skills of aimed shooting, and a professional will be able to bring their skills to perfection and hone their weapon skills.

Key features:
• Excellent practice for training accuracy;
• Many different tasks with different complexity;
• Detailed locations with the atmosphere of a real shooting range;
• Management with the Joy-Con™️ controllers;
